Anyway, he does not
like term limits.

00:09:25.740 --> 00:09:27.040
That's what I was talking about.

00:09:27.040 --> 00:09:28.370
&gt;&gt; Colleen Shogan: That's right.

00:09:28.370 --> 00:09:29.670
Right?

00:09:29.670 --> 00:09:31.280
&gt;&gt; Rep. Candice Miller: Anyway,
the-- so term limits it's you know,

00:09:31.280 --> 00:09:33.220
"nice job but drive thru."

00:09:33.220 --> 00:09:36.430
And so then I was trying to
decide, "Should I go back

00:09:36.430 --> 00:09:37.900
into the private sector
selling boats?

00:09:37.900 --> 00:09:39.200
Or doing something else?"

00:09:39.200 --> 00:09:42.120
And-- then I decided
to run for Congress.

00:09:42.120 --> 00:09:45.120
And so I came here the ra--
the race was in '02 [noise].

00:09:45.120 --> 00:09:48.880
I got-- I have the
microphone Mr. Ghost.

00:09:48.880 --> 00:09:50.180
&gt;&gt; Colleen Shogan: Right?

00:09:50.180 --> 00:09:52.720
&gt;&gt; Rep. Candice Miller: I came
here in '02, started in '03.

00:09:52.720 --> 00:09:55.860
And I have been here
